ins. The hooting of the ogres and the gentle lapping of the lake against the dock are the only sounds. Illuminated by the fire, a couple sits in protected comfort from the elements.<br>
<br>
Vaal sits in front of the campfire, the message from his friend in the Guardians of the Relics in his hands, a blank look in his eyes. He cannot believe what the letter states, but he trusts Fyona and knows she would never lie to him.<br>
<br>
He leans back against a rock, his thoughts a jumble, not even feeling the sharp points of stone digging into his back muscles. Evil inside the<br>
Guardians as guild members, the very thought makes him cringe. He remembers the night that Iumarie made him a guild member and his joy at discovering people that thought like he did. Vaal wonders how Faein, his hero, would feel about this change. Thinking about Faein brings back the names of other Guardians, lost in time, Kaeblizar, Nadenshadow, Dillard, and Shadowwulf. And Teysala how could he forget Teysala! Vaal remembers days long past when the voices of his friends would spring to life in his mind. He thinks about happier days with a longing in his heart.<br>
<br>
He passes the note to Lileah, his bride, and all he says is &quot;Necromancers and Shadow Knights are allowed to be Guardians now.&quot;  Vaal's voice catches on the words.<br>
<br>
Vaal slowly places a hand inside his tunic and retrieves his Guardians guild crest. Turning it over in his hand, he examines it carefully in the flickering light. He had worn it proudly for so long, always closest to his heart. Abruptly he tosses the crest into the fire, his dream of rejoining the Guardians turning to ash as the crest does. He mourns for what he lost, tears falling like rain from his eyes. The ogres hoot mournfully as if they share his loss.<br>
<br>
<br>
Vaal Khon'Elvair<br>
Paladin of Tunare <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.showMessage?topicID=66.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.showMessage?topicID=72.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.threadControl?topicID=74.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=74.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=74.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="brellserilisfrm48">Town Crier (Rules & Announcements)<option value="brellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion">The Commons (General EQ Discussion)<option value="brellserilisroleplaying">The Tavern (Roleplaying)<option value="brellserilisfrm66">Rants Link<option value="brellserilisfrm56">Salutations & Congratulations <option value="brellserilisfrm33">Dreams & Diversions (Off Topic)<option value="brellserilisfrm55">Fellowship of Guilds (Guildchat)<option value="brellserilisfrm64">Archived Threads<option value="brellserilisbrellslairadminonly">Brell's Lair (Admin only)<option value="brellserilismeleetalk">Tome: Races and Classes <option value="brellserilisfrm49">Tom